# Hospital Management System - Frontend Setup

## Environment Variables
Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure accordingly.

### Variables:
- `VITE_API_BASE_URL` - Base URL for API calls (default: http://localhost:8080/api)
- `VITE_HOSPITAL_API_BASE_URL` - Base URL for Hospital API v1 (default: http://localhost:9080)

Example:
```
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
VITE_HOSPITAL_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:9080
```

If using a production API:
```
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourhospital.com/api
VITE_HOSPITAL_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourhospital.com
```
